from dev.eclipse.org.. It fails for 7 test cases. The same test cases are 
failing on Mandrake Linux 9.2 also.
Please refer the attachments. I have also listed those failures here

Thanks
Jayaprakash

>I downloaded latest org.eclipse.cdt.core.test plugin from dev.eclipse.org.. 

From the head or 2.0 stream? There are changes being made in head that don't 
get applied to the 2.0 stream. Also, if you update the test plugin, make sure 
to update the rest of the plugins as well as changes might have gone in that 
will cause the suite to fail. I ran the test suite on the latest in the 2.0 
stream on XP and it passed.
These tests are passing in the weekly builds.
